title: The Totally Quirky Intro of Riri Williams (New Dr. Alpha Comic!)
description:
Dr. Alpha Dead Man's Lullaby: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/dr-alpha-dead-man-s-lullaby-vol-1/x/22169562#/

Brian Michael Bendis introduces us to the character of Riri Williams in a horrid mess of pros and spine tingling self-indulgence. But at least he knows his audience.
